headline: Dover Fueling Solutions Expands Wayne PWR DC Fast Charger Line to Accelerate EV Charging Deployment for Retail Fueling Sites
summary: Dover Fueling Solutions ("DFS"), a part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a leading global provider of advanced customer-focused technologies, services and solutions in the fuel and convenience retail industries, today announced the launch of four new power configurations for its Wayne PWR™ DC fast charger product line ranging from 160kW to 640kW.
